message:
I’ve fully implemented `run_exp1` in `main_vit.py`—capturing features, saving inputs & outputs, and plotting 3D visualizations via `lib.plot_3d_feat_vit`. Everything is localized to that function without touching other parts of the file. You can now run:

```
python -m unittest unit_test/unit_test_1.py
```

to verify that the new implementation passes the existing tests. Let me know if any issues come up!
